1.0.name: wordpress/ewire-payment-module-for-woocommerce
1.0.description: Ewire Payment Module for WooCoommerce makes it possible to accept payment from scandinavia. It is a simple setup. By adding this module to your setup you only need to create a Ewire Business account at http://www.ewire.dk/create. Afterwards you are ready to receive payments.
